    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/e58aa6088e3fbf9b258079af4a43ef9e.avif?t=1760549076\" width=600 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the role of an <strong>interior designer</strong> in a world in desperate need of creative touch...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ICONIC ISOMETRIC ARTSTYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a 3D world in an isometric point of view, capturing the charm of classic games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/67518839131fb590bcdbdbac4dc406b5.poster.avif?t=1760549076\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/67518839131fb590bcdbdbac4dc406b5.webm?t=1760549076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/67518839131fb590bcdbdbac4dc406b5.mp4?t=1760549076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>OVER 500 ITEMS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Almost every job unlocks something new to decorate with. Can you find all the hidden ones?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/a13597936a88fe5fdac0c985049b6b73.poster.avif?t=1760549076\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/a13597936a88fe5fdac0c985049b6b73.webm?t=1760549076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/a13597936a88fe5fdac0c985049b6b73.mp4?t=1760549076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RELAXING, YET REWARDING GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interior Tales offers a stress-free and forgiving gameplay experience while maintaining core simulation elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/879dcc7439b6de4e8f9025bb6d43579d.poster.avif?t=1760549076\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/879dcc7439b6de4e8f9025bb6d43579d.webm?t=1760549076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222920/extras/879dcc7439b6de4e8f9025bb6d43579d.mp4?t=1760549076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
